{{ko-hanja|hangeul=좌|rv=jwa|mr=chwa}}

# "Subordinate".
# "Commander". A field-grade officer in the Korean People's Army: Major (소좌; ''Sojwa'', or "Junior Commander"), Lieutenant-Colonel (중좌; ''Chungjwa'', or "Middle Commander"), Colonel (상좌; ''Sangjwa'', or "High Commander"), and Senior Colonel / Brigadier (대좌; ''Taejwa'', or "Grand Commander").
